## 7. Win Condition Rules (winCondition.ts — Phase 2.4)

### HEIR_ESCAPED
  Triggered when: character at EXIT_DOOR cell AND character.isPortraitHeir === true
  winner = playerId who controls that character
  winCondition = 'HEIR_ESCAPED'

### LAST_ALIVE
  Triggered when: only one player has at least one ALIVE character
  winner = that player
  winCondition = 'LAST_ALIVE'

### NON_HEIR_EXIT_ATTEMPT
  Character at EXIT_DOOR AND character.isPortraitHeir === false:
    → Do NOT eliminate the character
    → Reset position to 'FOYER'
    → Emit PAWN_RESET response (handled by transport layer)

