## 8. Testing Requirements for This Directory
  - Each engine module MUST have a corresponding spec file in src/__tests__/engine/
  - Spec naming: <moduleName>.spec.ts (e.g. playCard.spec.ts, winCondition.spec.ts)
  - All fixtures via src/__tests__/fixtures/gameState.fixtures.ts — no inline mocks
  - Minimum 10 test cases per engine module
  - Every EngineError.code must appear in at least one test as a negative case
  - Run `npx vitest run --reporter=verbose` and confirm full green before closing a phase
